episodes.title: Alleged Online Cult of Rashad Jamal with Mike King (Profiling Evil)
episodes.description:
The University of Cosmic Intelligence is allegedly an online cult, started by Rashad Jamal, 37, and has been linked to murders and missing people. There are six people missing, including two children, in Missouri, who have not been seen since August 2023, and their families are extremely concerned. 

Let's dive into what this alleged cult is all about, who Rashad Jamal is, and let's do our best to share information that might help locate the missing people. 

Today we are joined by Mike King from Profiling Evil, a cult expert with decades of law enforcement experience.
